title: [Wild Things, Euphoria]
description: White sheets of thick canvas hang from sturdy steel rods and cover the massive iron bars along the perimeter.  Filled with cattail and milkweed clusters, maoral boxes decorate the room, nearly hiding a small kennel and slatted crate that have been carefully tucked behind the planters.  Dangling precariously from a hook in the ceiling is a gilded bird cage, and a glass aquarium has been perched atop a sturdy table.
